'''Land area information''' is a tool that displays relevant information for any square of land on the map.

To get information for a square of land:

*Open the ''Other'' ([[File:en/Manual/Manual html 51cda05b.png|Other]]) menu and choose ''Land area information''
*Click on the section of land you want to display information for

